{"tid":1370450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敬告南亞朋友","createTime":"2019-07-27T04:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T04:08:21.000Z","uid":53735,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39049efd7af1287d651c5077964d381b1446335b","tid":1370450,"uid":53735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:06:15.000Z","msg":"陳雲：敬告南亞朋友，今日不要收錢在元朗毆打示威者。否則你們的兄弟姐妹在香港的命運將會非常坎坷。不單止民主政府對你們不利，現政府也會拿你們來做代罪羔羊，收緊福利、居留權及家庭團聚移民。請告訴鄉親，千萬不要做錯事，與收容國的人民為敵。<br />\n好似上次在長沙灣打藍絲的南亞青年，就做得好好，不要丟失他支持香港民主的一番心意。"},{"pid":"5200d34daf728edac48781f29042efaa80d8c2e8","tid":1370450,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"云伯收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n根本都有南亞人加入抗爭者行列<br />\n<br />\n你要POST云伯條仆街, 去高登POST啦"},{"pid":"1b995becd56610a94f6e6707a8514e68772e8090","tid":1370450,"uid":53735,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"有沒有人可以翻譯成其他語言？"},{"pid":"61c72f33aaeffcc87229cf9ccf9857d30a79a3dc","tid":1370450,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:07:20.000Z","msg":"云哥食藥未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad30dcf4f801f1da8dde17a818025c6d52472a48","tid":1370450,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"一粒老鼠屎就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8c1f074bffec3d10e0019698cf59d9d1f82a28","tid":1370450,"uid":61284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5200d34daf728edac48781f29042efaa80d8c2e8","tid":1370450,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"云伯收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n根本都有南亞人加入抗爭者行列<br />\n<br />\n你要POST云伯條仆街, 去高登POST啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"咁短都唔睇晒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4160e5ea6d45ed4945e793cd4